# 🎬 BlogTube

A full-stack video blogging platform where users can upload, view, like, comment, and manage their own videos.

---

* frontedgit:"https://chamithkumar.github.io/project-1/"
* backend: "https://project-1-2l4m.onrender.com"
*Netlify:"https://blogging-platform-amith.netlify.app/"


## 🚀 Features

* 🔐 User Authentication (JWT)
* 📤 Upload Videos
* ▶️ Play Videos
* 👍 Like System (instant update)
* 💬 Comment System
* 👁 View Counter
* ✏️ Edit Videos (only by owner)
* 🗑 Delete Videos (only by owner)
* 🔍 Search Videos
* 👤 User Profile with personal videos

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

### Frontend

* HTML
* CSS (Modern UI)
* JavaScript (Vanilla)

### Backend

* Node.js
* Express.js
* MongoDB (Mongoose)
* JWT Authentication
* Multer (file upload)

---

## 📁 Project Structure

```
BlogTube/
│
├── backend/
│   ├── models/
│   ├── routes/
│   ├── middleware/
│   └── server.js
│
├── frontend/
│   ├── index.html
│   ├── style.css
│   └── script.js
```

---

## ⚙️ Setup Instructions

### 1. Clone Repository

```
git clone https://github.com/your-username/blogtube.git
cd blogtube
```

---

### 2. Backend Setup

```
cd backend
npm install
```

Create `.env` file:

```
MONGO_URI=your_mongodb_url
JWT_SECRET=your_secret_key
```

Run server:

```
node server.js
```

---

### 3. Frontend Setup

Just open:

```
index.html
```

---

## 🌐 Deployment

### Backend (Render)

* Hosted on Render
* Uses environment variables

### Frontend (Netlify)

* Static hosting

